'''Tulmon''' was a small independent city-state in the [[Arnaden (region)|Arnaden]] region.{{Cite web/More Lake of Steam and Dragon Coast}}

{{Quote|We'll ignore the spells you have the good taste not to cast, but before you think to topple towers, think on this: Just how
many hurled stones can your spells ward away or blast aside? We have a ''lot'' of stones.|A famous Tulmonite warning towards [[wizard]]s, originating from the play ''[[The Red Rages of Ozoone Stormspells]]''.<ref name=EotSS-p166">}}
